org.fudgemsg.types
Class FudgeTime

java.lang.Object
  org.fudgemsg.types.FudgeTime

public class FudgeTime
extends java.lang.Object

Dummy class for holding a time value on its own, as Java does not have a standard type for doing so. See DateTime encoding for more details.
